" MCHA fields: WERKS, CHARG, ERSDA, ERNAM, LAEDA, AENAM, BWTAR, LIFNR, LWEDT, HERKL
"
" Note: Original instructions say BRGEW, NTGEW, GEWEI, VOLUM, VOLEH come from MCHA.
" However these fields don't exist in MCHA in our training system.
" Verified in SE11 — they are in MARA. SELECT retrieves them from MARA (alias a).
